	<p>SurgeViewer is a data visualization and filtering web application to be used in-house use by Bombora, the leading provider of B2B demographic, firmographic and Intent data.</p>
    <p>Our tool is intended to aid Bombora&#8217;s sales staff in determining changing trends of topics which are important to their potential customers, by automatically charting new data as it is received.  This tool will help to quickly determine which Bombora customers are invested in selected topics, and it will give its users to filter content to focus in on particular topics or company attributes.</p>
