    <p><span style="font-weight:400;">This is a patent of gathering and using consumer purchasing intent. Purchasing intent is gather from text, audio and image data. The data from audio and image is extracted using speech recognition and character recognition respectively. The data is stored in a database which will be used by a computer to enhance the consumer’s shopping experience.</span></p>

